The following commit has been merged into the irq/irqchip-next branch of irqchip:

Commit-ID:     046a6ee2343bb26d85a9973a39ccdb9764236fa4
Gitweb:        https://git.kernel.org/pub/scm/linux/kernel/git/maz/arm-platforms/046a6ee2343bb26d85a9973a39ccdb9764236fa4
Author:        Marc Zyngier <maz@kernel.org>
AuthorDate:    Tue, 04 May 2021 17:42:18 +01:00
Committer:     Marc Zyngier <maz@kernel.org>
CommitterDate: Thu, 10 Jun 2021 13:09:19 +01:00

irqchip: Bulk conversion to generic_handle_domain_irq()

Wherever possible, replace constructs that match either
generic_handle_irq(irq_find_mapping()) or
generic_handle_irq(irq_linear_revmap()) to a single call to
generic_handle_domain_irq().

Reviewed-by: Geert Uytterhoeven <geert+renesas@glider.be>
Acked-by: Krzysztof Kozlowski <krzysztof.kozlowski@canonical.com>
Signed-off-by: Marc Zyngier <maz@kernel.org>
---
